:Feline:
She looked down at her, "I have no faction.  So I shall join yours."
She stood up on the branch and lept down to the ground and stood next 
to Reptilica. She transformed into bot mode and stood there.
"So, where is your place of opperations? Will you show me?"
She could smell another bot near by, but not see it.  She figured the 
male counter part of this female bot was cloaked somewhere near by, 
watching.  
"Please, take me to your base."

> ::Reptilica/DevilDuer::
>

> 
> "I'm with the Alliance, the superior faction. Which faction are you 
part of?"
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> Cloaked, DevilDuer looks at Feline from behind a few bushes. If she 
made any
